      "id": "s3_col1_rect_text",
      "x": 80, "y": 1980, "width": 600, "height": 60,
      "text": "create_llm_client(provider, model, *, auth_mode)\nLazy imports • OpenAI / Anthropic / Google / Azure / xAI / DeepSeek / Qwen / GLM\nOAuth read-only (Anthropic, OpenAI) • Cross-provider rate-limit retry",
      "originalText": "create_llm_client(provider, model, *, auth_mode)\nLazy imports • OpenAI / Anthropic / Google / Azure / xAI / DeepSeek / Qwen / GLM\nOAuth read-only (Anthropic, OpenAI) • Cross-provider rate-limit retry",
      "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3,
